@{"GUESSBOOTDEV" link "GUIDEDIR:Other/GUESSBOOTDEV.help/MAIN"}     Identifies the bootable volume's name.

@{"HDTOOLBOX" link "GUIDEDIR:Tools/HDTOOLBOX.guide/MAIN"}        Hard drive partitioning tool.
@{"HELP" link "GUIDEDIR:System/HELP.help/MAIN"}             Pops up the built-in AmigaOS help subsystem.
