@{"HISTORY" link "GUIDEDIR:Commands/HISTORY.help/MAIN"}          Displays the history of commands.

@{"ICONEDIT" link "GUIDEDIR:Tools/ICONEDIT.help/MAIN"}         Edits the appearance and type of icons.
@{"ICONX" link "GUIDEDIR:Commands/ICONX.help/MAIN"}            Allows execution of a script file from an icon.
@{"IF" link "GUIDEDIR:Commands/IF.help/MAIN"}               Evaluates conditional operations in script files.
@{"INFO" link "GUIDEDIR:Commands/INFO.help/MAIN"}             Reports information about the file system(s).
@{"INITPRINTER" link "GUIDEDIR:Tools/INITPRINTER.help/MAIN"}      Initializes a printer according to its prefs.
@{"INSTALL" link "GUIDEDIR:Commands/INSTALL.help/MAIN"}          Writes a boot block to a floppy disk or PCMCIA card.
@{"INSTALLER" link "GUIDEDIR:System/INSTALLER.help/MAIN"}        Script based default installation utility.
@{"INTELLIFONT" link "GUIDEDIR:System/INTELLIFONT.help/MAIN"}      Runs the Intellifont program to manage outline fonts.
@{"IPREFS" link "GUIDEDIR:Commands/IPREFS.help/MAIN"}           Sends preferences to the Workbench and Intuition.

@{"JOIN" link "GUIDEDIR:Commands/JOIN.help/MAIN"}             Concatenates two or more files into a new file.

@{"KEYSHOW" link "GUIDEDIR:Tools/KEYSHOW.help/MAIN"}          Displays the current keyboard keymap.

@{"LAB" link "GUIDEDIR:Commands/LAB.help/MAIN"}              Specifies a label in a script file.
