@{"LOADWB" link "GUIDEDIR:Commands/LOADWB.help/MAIN"}           Starts Workbench.
@{"LOCK" link "GUIDEDIR:Commands/LOCK.help/MAIN"}             Sets the write protect status of a device.

@{"MAKEDIR" link "GUIDEDIR:Commands/MAKEDIR.help/MAIN"}          Creates a new directory.
@{"MAKELINK" link "GUIDEDIR:Commands/MAKELINK.help/MAIN"}         Creates a link between files.
